{
  "3009310": {
    "name": "弈战征途",
    "steam_appid": 3009310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/6f657711e7b573f0a8c5cb17f224ddbe.avif?t=1770862650\" width=780 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《弈战征途》是一款受经典桌游启发的构筑式肉鸽游戏，规则简明却蕴含深度策略。在被黑色迷雾笼罩的世界中，你将率领自己的雇佣兵小队踏上远征，揭开黑暗深处隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/4dd8fcd3a5f03b2fd53f456474f36b29.poster.avif?t=1770862650\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/4dd8fcd3a5f03b2fd53f456474f36b29.webm?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/4dd8fcd3a5f03b2fd53f456474f36b29.mp4?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化你的战术，部署雇佣兵，引领他们走向胜利。强化单位、组合特质，构筑强力的协同体系——唯有如此，才能在前方危机四伏的旅途中存活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作虽上手容易，但真正精通需要洞察与经验。我们期待看到你以缜密的策略与创造性的解法，征服前方的一切挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回合制自动战斗 · 规则简单</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/260f25b308a14883c2818b1373099d01.poster.avif?t=1770862650\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/260f25b308a14883c2818b1373099d01.webm?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/260f25b308a14883c2818b1373099d01.mp4?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一回合，你需要消耗行动点，将佣兵部署到战场上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦战斗开始，佣兵将根据各自的速度自动行动，因此在部署阶段合理站位至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗结构虽然直观，胜负却取决于对所有影响战局要素的综合判断——技能、地形障碍、旗帜耐久度以及状态效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次错误的判断，便可能彻底改变战斗的走向，请谨慎决策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组合技能、神器与传闻，构筑无尽策略</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/fd4c7717b49bfc96f484d4a709670167.avif?t=1770862650\" width=780 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《弈战征途》的设计追求直观易懂，却要求玩家具备高度的战略思考能力——你需要组合佣兵技能、管理神器，并优化指挥官的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这种设计让“易上手”与“高深度”得以并存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你招募的不是卡牌，而是佣兵棋子，并在组建远征队的过程中逐步构筑你的“牌库”。每名雇佣兵都拥有在战斗中触发的独特技能，且最多可同时组合两种技能，从而衍生出近乎无限的协同可能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/af3e8dad421f1eb98c15d48dfb0ce5d5.poster.avif?t=1770862650\" width=1170 height=620 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/af3e8dad421f1eb98c15d48dfb0ce5d5.webm?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/af3e8dad421f1eb98c15d48dfb0ce5d5.mp4?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/c9e6b7c0201d04f28e7ef0e2c5736fb4.poster.avif?t=1770862650\" width=1170 height=620 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/c9e6b7c0201d04f28e7ef0e2c5736fb4.webm?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/c9e6b7c0201d04f28e7ef0e2c5736fb4.mp4?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着队伍不断成长并取得胜利，关于他们的传闻也会逐渐流传——正如昔日的传奇战士一般。传闻将赋予特殊能力，与技能或升级系统相互独立。若你的某名雇佣兵声名远扬，便可前往酒馆散播其事迹，进一步放大队伍的整体协同效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>失败，并非终点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/74b79b78a8ca742ba425803804919698.avif?t=1770862650\" width=780 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片残酷的世界中，你的旅程或许会以失败告终——但每一次失败，都是孕育新可能的种子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 100 种佣兵与技能、30 件神器、20 张卡牌，确保每一次远征都是独一无二的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以利用失败远征中获得的资源，在前哨基地建造设施。这些建筑将提供永久性强化：更多可用道具、更强的佣兵，以及其他能在未来旅途中发挥关键作用的优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建筑事件 · 为强敌做好准备</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/cfaab42696a77e1e336eb0b96516e542.poster.avif?t=1770862650\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/cfaab42696a77e1e336eb0b96516e542.webm?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/cfaab42696a77e1e336eb0b96516e542.mp4?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/03b5183359fd2d74e592b27d4f31608d.poster.avif?t=1770862650\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/03b5183359fd2d74e592b27d4f31608d.webm?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/03b5183359fd2d74e592b27d4f31608d.mp4?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各个区域中，你会遭遇不同的建筑事件：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在此组合技能、遣散多余的佣兵、购买神器或道具，为接下来的战斗做好充分准备。不断壮大自身，迎战前方等待你的强大邪恶势力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>旅途中的未知事件</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/63f2aa3dd53e7e79022f432642c59bc2.poster.avif?t=1770862650\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/63f2aa3dd53e7e79022f432642c59bc2.webm?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009310/extras/63f2aa3dd53e7e79022f432642c59bc2.mp4?t=1770862650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真正艰难的抉择，并不只发生在战斗中。旅途中，你将遭遇随机的卡牌事件——简短却意味深长的故事，你的选择将直接决定结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的决策，究竟会为远征带来机遇，还是将队伍推向深渊？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为指挥官，整个小队的命运，掌握在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 韩语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 俄语, 日语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲",
